{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":3678255,"name":"Boyu","username":"Zeonica","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/zeonica/{size}/266380_2.png","created_at":"2025-07-10T16:36:21.182Z","cooked":"<p>I am working on our robot‚Äôs elevator subsystem, and we‚Äôre running into a persistent issue where our REV throughbore encoder always reads 0, regardless of whether the elevator is moving. We‚Äôve tried various debugging steps, but haven‚Äôt found a solution yet. We‚Äôre using java and connect with RoboRIO DIO ports 8 and 9.</p>
<p>Here‚Äôs the code<br>
